{"tid":1798360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"PaulPogba：有冇人成日有偉大想法，但次次都未開始就放棄？","createTime":"2019-12-26T07:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T03:17:54.000Z","uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20d039ff93328c0e9c1fc7ac8c477320ba8ff1be","tid":1798360,"uid":251052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"中學暗戀個女同學，幾乎鼓起勇氣表白，但最後都係唔敢<br />\n諗住認真讀書，然後覺得好辛苦，都係打機好玩<br />\n想做LOL職業選手，但輸幾場就覺得冇可能<br />\n我好鍾意睇小說，有次又幻想自己可以成為村上咁既作家，最後當然又放棄咗，與其話係放棄 倒不如話根本冇開始過<br />\n到出黎做嘢<br />\n本來打算學一門手藝做個匠人，結果偷懶比人炒咗<br />\n依家做緊保安<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己好似madao<br />\n我既人生只差一步就可以變得好美好"},{"pid":"df3899f97d65bfa9cc45919a452a21339f9ac4c0","tid":1798360,"uid":206024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T07:17:43.000Z","msg":"stay hungry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03031c2ab7da256328da8b9cd9db8558871cbf95","tid":1798360,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"我差一步就可以跳落去"},{"pid":"4911f77422cc82a8f477ab8d07d689d76f1cc3ec","tid":1798360,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03031c2ab7da256328da8b9cd9db8558871cbf95","tid":1798360,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"我差一步就可以跳落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"你諗住用前腳跳先定後腳跳先"},{"pid":"07eb9797cda99585986e2e5fff5027aeded84fa1","tid":1798360,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4911f77422cc82a8f477ab8d07d689d76f1cc3ec","tid":1798360,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03031c2ab7da256328da8b9cd9db8558871cbf95","tid":1798360,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:45:34.000Z","msg":"我差一步就可以跳落去"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:57:34.000Z","msg":"你諗住用前腳跳先定後腳跳先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T11:59:06.000Z","msg":"你四隻腳 唔會明我兩隻腳點跳"},{"pid":"6f44